{"tid":403934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好重視承諾","createTime":"2017-09-17T14:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T02:39:34.000Z","uid":129039,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62ed17af1f4c000bfe551eedc77d9b6bdbf85cab","tid":403934,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"唔只係話婚姻要一生一世 直到海枯石爛 呢啲&quot;大嘅&quot;承諾<br />\n一啲比較平凡 冇咁重要嘅事都好重視<br />\n例如如果講好今晚要去邊度食飯 就死都要去 唔係去嗰度嘅話個心就會唔舒服，約咗個fd一陣五點等 就算有更緊急嘅野做 都寧願去赴會 因為已經應承咗，如果我應承咗個fd今日幫佢入數 就算幾唔得耐都會死落樓㩒atm入數，話咗要做嘅話就算好小事都一定要完成<br />\n但感覺好似冇乜人已經重視承諾 係咪得番我咁傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48c320056108d5a371a3d682047b21df147745c","tid":403934,"uid":112123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"認承完再做埋<br />\n但係接受個位唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d26feb66b4a6ea5310b4eb86aecbb2eb1e337c7","tid":403934,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:53:00.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f5f36bd85599d9768cbafd35cd0d2286382b1c","tid":403934,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"假如<br />\n兩個承諾有抵觸呢🤔"},{"pid":"0ca311db5d8605f76664ae18d8b69b275d3f0e50","tid":403934,"uid":14705,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"巴打同我一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我應承左人既野一定會做 做唔到唔會應承 我會睇唔起講完又唔撚做既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6346abd0c1c26588f8f50c928e1c06f811cfe938","tid":403934,"uid":14705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假如<br />\n兩個承諾有抵觸呢🤔</blockquote><br />\n你知道有抵觸 咁一定唔會許下第二個承諾"},{"pid":"b1d9be305c976fab97494d3763f93285ea96fdcb","tid":403934,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>假如<br />\n兩個承諾有抵觸呢🤔</blockquote><br />\n你知道有抵觸 咁一定唔會許下第二個承諾</blockquote><br />\n假如<br />\n係應承果剎那互不抵觸呢🤔"},{"pid":"2245772e9a855a54af51a5c1b07c84d6a77ba326","tid":403934,"uid":119363,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"就算花光心機守每一個諾言，最後誰又會可憐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bb88d229e8078ce2ed6a3e3cb3009dda50b7e6","tid":403934,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認承完再做埋<br />\n但係接受個位唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喺呢一刻終於明白到原來自己做嘅野根本冇人重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2931804a4cada9249b8adca6a9c46f1939c32e8b","tid":403934,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d9ba338ae4c70d0ebf241fb53f58d909b2987e","tid":403934,"uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:23:26.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n做唔到唔好講<br />\n寧願冇俾過希望出黎"},{"pid":"8b31cc19a89c5066740c82739ec4f1da423402c7","tid":403934,"uid":56790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:24:23.000Z","msg":"尤其對自己的承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc87d385c13df721549ba1cd872bb0b2f3290888","tid":403934,"uid":31007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尤其對自己的承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger ~ <img src