mal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger ~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係咪有咩想分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd48921ff7028d3eadcb0c79057bb8938c277cc","tid":403934,"uid":90165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"我重視 曾經同一名識左十幾年網友 講過 <br />\n佢結婚時 一定會出現(結婚前 未見過對方)<br />\n當佢結婚果日 我真係去左 個感覺好神奇 <br />\n個人會好開心 因為完成到一個承諾"},{"pid":"0ecfdc7aa5064fdb6e801bc9bd4e851068fdc2d6","tid":403934,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>假如<br />\n兩個承諾有抵觸呢🤔</blockquote><br />\n你知道有抵觸 咁一定唔會許下第二個承諾</blockquote><br />\n假如<br />\n係應承果剎那互不抵觸呢🤔</blockquote><br />\n世紀難題咁嘅款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇情況啦 盡量兩個都做到 唔得嘅就做應承先嗰個先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f940cccd36d508f59e2c519196ee2cd80bb3f1d","tid":403934,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n做唔到寧願唔講<br />\n好少放飛機 除非係病得好嚴重或者出大事"},{"pid":"e76fe38811091105a371e2b8e261f0c54f22b404","tid":403934,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我重視 曾經同一名識左十幾年網友 講過 <br />\n佢結婚時 一定會出現(結婚前 未見過對方)<br />\n當佢結婚果日 我真係去左 個感覺好神奇 <br />\n個人會好開心 因為完成到一個承諾</blockquote><br />\n巴打好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都想有朋友可以咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98984ca8576a7148976469fcfbcdb52a776696d0","tid":403934,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我<br />\n做唔到寧願唔講<br />\n好少放飛機 除非係病得好嚴重或者出大事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bf90071708191f829ab501eccd2349b4c87d9a","tid":403934,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我<br />\n做唔到唔好講<br />\n寧願冇俾過希望出黎</blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n所以成日都唔會應承人 就算係啲好小嘅事都好 唔係100%確定得嘅都唔會應承 一應承咗就好似有舊石落喺自己膊頭度咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到你真係做唔到就做唔到嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 聽過啦呢句<br />\nsor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 激動咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b49c8f7019e65850e7d0b63df81e6dbaf894dd","tid":403934,"uid":139226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"就係因為重視 <br />\n自己作出承諾嗰時會好小心好驚做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係因為咁 對方應承左嘅嘢結果做唔到 會好心淡 同唔想再將人地對自己嘅承諾睇得咁重 唔想又再失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243148bcbc65c07da30cf35901601bad175b4dbd","tid":403934,"uid":106569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔只係話婚姻要一生一世 直到海枯石爛 呢啲&quot;大嘅&quot;承諾<br />\n一啲比較平凡 冇咁重要嘅事都好重視<br />\n例如如果講好今晚要去邊度食飯 就死都要去 唔係去嗰度嘅話個心就會唔舒服，約咗個fd一陣五點等 就算有更緊急嘅野做 都寧願去赴會 因為已經應承咗，如果我應承咗個fd今日幫佢入數 就算幾唔得耐都會死落樓㩒atm入數，話咗要做嘅話就算好小事都一定要完成<br />\n但感覺好似冇乜人已經重視承諾 係咪得番我咁傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n分左手之後先痛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664d1aedb22c4992022b362607e43961ecff5129","tid":403934,"uid":27830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"做唔到就唔好講"},{"pid":"69fe76ed5d3f68f462a9976c3c249706a04e22e4","tid":403934,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:41:05.000Z","msg":"就係因為重視承諾,所以好難對其他人作出承諾"},{"pid":"73d703e5cc77cb8c9c4a5c727b653b846a89ec39","tid":403934,"uid":112439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl